title: 108. What is for you, is for YOU
description:
Happy Thursday!

In this episode we talk all things why what is for you is for YOU. If you desire it, it HAS to come to pass. It has to pop up in the physical. Period. Listen to this episode to find out just what I am talking about.

Click here to enroll in my 4 month group coaching program The Embodied Womxn (3 spots left!) or visit Beatricekamau.com/embodiedwomxn
